data.title: Prince Rashid bin Hassan
data.meta_description: Prince Rashid bin El Hassan is a member of the Jordanian royal family. He is the only son of Prince Hassan bin Talal and Princess Sarvath al-Hassan and is a first cousin of King Abdullah II.
